How to link an HTML file with PHP file

Create a file named as index.html inside document root then
Type below code

<html>
<body>
<form action=”welcome.php” method=”post”>
NAME <input type=”text” name=”name”><br>
ID <input type”text” name=”id”><br>
<input type=”submit”>
</form>
</body>
</html>



Now create a file welcome.php  inside document root and type below code 

<html>
<body>
NAME IS : <?php echo $_POST[“name”]; ?> <br>
ID IS : <?php echo $_POST[“id”]; ?> 
</body>
</html>


Output will be like below
 

NAME IS : ARUN
ID IS : 1000
